name: Dalhousie Chess Club

description: Helped create a website from scratch for the Dalhousie Chess Club. My role was a junior developer and some of the contributions I did was creating the navbar, footer, organizers information page (about page).

name: QuickCash App
author: David W.
description: I am currently developing an Android app that deals with employers being able to post jobs for potential employee, and said employees searching for jobs. I am a developer in this project and some of the contributions I did was create the signup page, a search bar and filtering for searching for jobs.
